{
  "message": "Enhance README and ubs script with new features and documentation\n\n- Added 'easy-mode' installation option for automatic dependency setup in README.md.\n- Introduced on-device agent guardrails for various coding agents, detailing integration in README.md.\n- Updated ubs script banner for improved visibility and branding.\n- Enhanced documentation for AI workflows and agent integration benefits.\n\nThese changes improve user experience and streamline the installation process for new users.",
